---
// CTA Section - Call to action for getting started with RootSpec
---

<section data-test="cta-section" class="cta">
  <div class="cta-container">
    <h2 class="cta-title">Ready to Build with Philosophy?</h2>

    <p class="cta-description">
      Join developers who are building software where philosophy guides implementation. Start with <strong>getting started</strong> documentation or explore our community.
    </p>

    <div class="cta-actions">
      <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/rootspec" data-test="github-link" class="cta-primary">
        <svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" class="github-icon">
          <path d="M12 0C5.374 0 0 5.373 0 12 0 17.302 3.438 21.8 8.207 23.387c.599.111.793-.261.793-.577v-2.234c-3.338.726-4.033-1.416-4.033-1.416-.546-1.387-1.333-1.756-1.333-1.756-1.089-.745.083-.729.083-.729 1.205.084 1.839 1.237 1.839 1.237 1.07 1.834 2.807 1.304 3.492.997.107-.775.418-1.305.762-1.604-2.665-.305-5.467-1.334-5.467-5.931 0-1.311.469-2.381 1.236-3.221-.124-.303-.535-1.524.117-3.176 0 0 1.008-.322 3.301 1.23A11.509 11.509 0 0112 5.803c1.02.005 2.047.138 3.006.404 2.291-1.552 3.297-1.23 3.297-1.23.653 1.653.242 2.874.118 3.176.77.84 1.235 1.911 1.235 3.221 0 4.609-2.807 5.624-5.479 5.921.43.372.823 1.102.823 2.222v3.293c0 .319.192.694.801.576C20.566 21.797 24 17.3 24 12c0-6.627-5.373-12-12-12z"/>
        </svg>
        View on GitHub
      </a>

      <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/rootspec#getting-started" class="cta-secondary">
        Documentation
      </a>
    </div>

    <div data-test="community-links" class="community-links">
      <h3 class="community-title">Community & Resources</h3>
      <div class="community-grid">
        <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/demos" class="community-link">
          <span class="community-link-title">Demo Projects</span>
          <span class="community-link-description">Explore real implementations</span>
        </a>

        <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/rootspec/discussions" class="community-link">
          <span class="community-link-title">Discussions</span>
          <span class="community-link-description">Ask questions, share ideas</span>
        </a>

        <a href="https://github.com/rootspec/rootspec/issues" class="community-link">
          <span class="community-link-title">Issues</span>
          <span class="community-link-description">Report bugs, request features</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
.cta {
  padding: var(--space-64) 0;
  background: var(--color-background);
  text-align: center;
}

.cta-container {
  max-width: 800px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: 0 var(--space-16);
}

.cta-title {
  font-size: var(--text-3xl);
  font-weight: 700;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-16);
  color: var(--color-text);
}

.cta-description {
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-32);
  line-height: 1.6;
}

.cta-actions {
  display: flex;
  gap: var(--space-16);
  justify-content: center;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-48);
  flex-wrap: wrap;
}

.cta-primary {
  background: var(--color-primary);
  color: white;
  padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-24);
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  gap: var(--space-8);
  transition: background-color 200ms ease;
  min-width: 160px;
  justify-content: center;
}

.cta-primary:hover {
  background: var(--color-primary-hover);
}

.cta-secondary {
  background: transparent;
  color: var(--color-text);
  padding: var(--space-12) var(--space-24);
  border: 2px solid var(--color-border);
  border-radius: 8px;
  text-decoration: none;
  font-weight: 600;
  transition: all 200ms ease;
  min-width: 160px;
  display: flex;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: center;
}

.cta-secondary:hover {
  background: var(--color-surface-elevated);
  border-color: var(--color-primary);
}

.github-icon {
  width: 20px;
  height: 20px;
}

.community-links {
  border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  padding-top: var(--space-32);
}

.community-title {
  font-size: var(--text-lg);
  font-weight: 600;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-24);
  color: var(--color-text);
}

.community-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
  gap: var(--space-16);
}

.community-link {
  display: flex;
  flex-direction: column;
  align-items: center;
  text-decoration: none;
  padding: var(--space-16);
  border-radius: 8px;
  background: var(--color-surface-elevated);
  border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  transition: all 200ms ease;
}

.community-link:hover {
  background: var(--color-background);
  border-color: var(--color-primary);
  transform: translateY(-2px);
}

.community-link-title {
  font-weight: 600;
  color: var(--color-text);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-4);
}

.community-link-description {
  font-size: var(--text-sm);
  color: var(--color-text-secondary);
}

@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .cta {
    padding: var(--space-48) 0;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .cta-primary,
  .cta-secondary {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 280px;
  }

  .community-grid {
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
  }

  .community-link:hover {
    transform: none;
  }
}

/* Reduce motion for accessibility */
@media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
  .cta-primary,
  .cta-secondary,
  .community-link {
    transition: none !important;
  }

  .community-link:hover {
    transform: none !important;
  }
}
</style>